The paper proposes a new recurrent cell for RNNs that is more computationally efficient and robust against vanishing or exploding gradients. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV).
